OK, you clicked here thinking that I was providing the top 10 list.<br>
<br>
SO first I apologize, as i do not know, am a couple levels from poison skill still.<br>
<br>
Its a question to the master thieves out there who care to respond and help a fellow aspiring assasin.<br>
<br>
If you had to pick a handful of poisons to utilize in pvp, which would they be?<br>
<br>
perhaps theres not 10, but i was thinking of a &quot;first do this then raise skill to this, then later in levels use this, <br>
<br>
but these are the always useful stand bys<br>
<br>
